{"tid":2330974,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"粉絲問「少女時代何時回歸」　秀英答覆引發期待！","createTime":"2020-12-18T11:52:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T05:11:18.000Z","uid":16659,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d79052e283aff6e19152b21302a4714e1a7681e3","tid":2330974,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T11:52:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_3eec5a5f588e0e6a73eaf21b5b6c3607/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-18/132426-889516.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_3eec5a5f588e0e6a73eaf21b5b6c3607%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-18%2F132426-889516.png&h=78f5dcbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然暫停團體活動好幾年，少女時代的好感情依然有目共睹，今天秀英的一段話更點燃了 SONE 的熱烈期待！<br />\n<br />\n秀英今天（18 日）代班主持 KBS Cool FM 的廣播節目《鄭恩地的歌謠廣場》，席間被聽眾問及「少女時代什麼時候會回歸」時，秀英先親切地說道：「跟我們一起成長的『少女時代世代』都過得還好嗎？我們很快地就會來問候大家。」雖然沒有明確透露回歸消息，依然令粉絲期待不已。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_74b9f91cf615ec47cf48c05350d4124a/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-18/132426-889517.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_74b9f91cf615ec47cf48c05350d4124a%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-18%2F132426-889517.png&h=b81626bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不僅如此，秀英還在節目中與 Tiffany 連線，Tiffany 搞笑道：「其實我平常都在 1 秒內就接起來，剛剛故意拖延，讓妳焦急一下。」還透露：「本來少女時代預定在年底聚會的，但為了安全起見，所以就取消了。」<br />\n<br />\n節目播出後，許多粉絲紛紛討論「真的假的？要回歸了嗎？」、「好想趕快看到少女時代」。少女時代目前的最後一張團體作品〈Holiday Night〉，距離如今已有三年之久，真的很期待能聽見好消息啊！"},{"pid":"a752818eee18704d9ff3ad228ab961c1a5a414f1","tid":2330974,"uid":93096,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T11:54:52.000Z","msg":"永遠是！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03650cb49e1176725d58fb497f5917119c8f22e2","tid":2330974,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":19,"score":-18,"quote":{"pid":"a752818eee18704d9ff3ad228ab961c1a5a414f1","tid":2330974,"uid":93096,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTim